<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">This is a call for all Necros out there (especially on Cazik Thule).<p>

I have been grouping with many many necros and I made one observation: 90% of the necros I played with are so bad its not even funny anymore.<br>
I am a SK at 21 and with a necro in a group I should mostly be a tank... well should...<p>

Just let me tell you some of the no-no's I have seen out there and if you catch yourself doing one of those things<br>
please stop doing them or remove yourself from the group otherwise others will do it for you and the necro rep suffers again.<p>

1. Pet is walking UP and down during a fight ... (how about if you set it on guard spot or send it in)<br>
2. If you see the SK getting a clinging darkness out and your DOT is not there yet you were way to slow...<br>
3. Fear mobs during fight... and they come back with a whole train of baddies<br>
4. Loot in between casts.. and not in between fights... (many gnomes were seen to do that)<br>
5. Cast on mezmerized MOBs (at least you are dead, unless the tank gets the mob off you and the MOB who he was fighting goes for the cleric and kills him, no matter if your pet yells Taunting attacker...)<br>
6. Have damaged mobs run away (without darkness). (Necro asks where is my pet) Pet kills mob. Trains SG gets killed and SG comes after the whole group with 0 warning so all dead. <p>

If you have ever done things like that eiter:<br>
1. WORK HARD on not doing stuff like that anymore.<br>
2. Stop playing a necro because you cause more death in your own rows than with your enemies...<p>

AND RULE #1, IF YOU THINK YOU ARE A REAL BADA** SO YOU NEED TO PLAY NECRO... THAT IS WRONG!!!<br>
ONLY IF YOU KNOW HOW TO PLAY AND ARE REALLY GOOD AT WHAT YOU ARE DOING YOU SHOULD GO FOR A NECRO.<p>

So if there is any necro out there who really knows what he is doing give me a HAIL in Cazik Thule...<hr>Terrora <br>
The hottest Shadow Knight lady on Cazic-Thule</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
